# UI Components

This document outlines the UI components used throughout the Watermark Editor application.

## Chakra UI Components

The application uses Chakra UI with custom wrappers for consistency and theming:

- [src/components/ui/provider.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/provider.tsx): Main provider component for Chakra UI
- [src/components/ui/color-mode.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/color-mode.tsx): Color mode (light/dark) management

### Form Components
- [src/components/ui/input-group.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/input-group.tsx): Input group component
- [src/components/ui/field.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/field.tsx): Form field wrapper
- [src/components/ui/checkbox.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/checkbox.tsx): Checkbox component
- [src/components/ui/radio.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/radio.tsx): Radio button component
- [src/components/ui/slider.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/slider.tsx): Slider component

### Overlay Components
- [src/components/ui/dialog.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/dialog.tsx): Dialog modal component
- [src/components/ui/drawer.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/drawer.tsx): Drawer component
- [src/components/ui/popover.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/popover.tsx): Popover component
- [src/components/ui/tooltip.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/tooltip.tsx): Tooltip component

### Display Components
- [src/components/ui/avatar.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/avatar.tsx): Avatar display component
- [src/components/ui/close-button.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/close-button.tsx): Close button component
